    "analysis of certain behaviors using software like OpenFace (6), OpenPose (7) or Movement Analysis (MEA; [8] [9] [10] [11].",
    "Through certain algorithms, such software quantifies the amount of nonverbal behavior which is present in the videos, thus facilitating the measurement of synchrony profoundly.",
    "In psychotherapeutic research, movement synchrony is typically measured by MEA (3, 8).",
    "Computer algorithms calculate the movement energy as the amount of pixel changes between picture frames.",
    "Then, cross-correlations between this quantified movement energy are calculated to find covariations in the movements between interactants within a time-lag of between 0 sec and 10 sec."
